            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName>Sigifridi qui Bonitio vocatur</persName> del fu
                            <persName>Gosberto</persName> vende all’<rs key="#Archpriests"
                            >arciprete</rs>
                        <persName key="#Archpriests">Pietro</persName> figlio della fu
                            <persName>Anna</persName> tutte le <rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie"
                            >casis et rebus massariciis</rs> che possiede infra <rs key="#Comitatus"
                            >comitato et terreturio</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/154"><placeName ref="#places/273"
                                >Roselle</placeName></geogName> in loco et finibus <placeName
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie" ref="#places/272">Nussina</placeName>
                        con la sua porzione de <rs key="#Churches">cappella</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches">Sancti Martini</orgName> e tutte le loro
                        dipendenze, <rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">casis et rebus
                            massariciis</rs> poste in [l]oco <placeName
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie" ref="#places/288">Sassi</placeName>; in
                        loco ubi dicitur <placeName key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie"
                            ref="#places/271">Pratello</placeName>; e in loco <placeName
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">Castria</placeName> poste infra <rs
                            key="#Comitatus">comitato et terreturio</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/107">Voloterrensis</geogName>, con
                        tutte le loro dipendenze, per il prezzo di 100 soldi d’argento. Chiede al
                            <rs key="#Notary">notaio</rs> regio <persName key="#Notary"
                            >Fermo</persName> la stesura della cartula. Actum loco <placeName
                            ref="#places/270">Tabiano</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Comitatus">terreturio</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/154">Rosellenses</geogName>.
                        Testimoni: <persName>Rainaldo</persName>; <persName>Acio</persName>;
                            <persName>Camarino</persName>; <persName>Eriberto</persName>.</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
